<view class="page voice-page">
  <view class="page-head floral-title-box title-pattern-card"><image class="title-pattern-image" src="/assets/tabbar-source/light-pink.png" mode="aspectFill" /><view class="title-pattern-mask"></view><view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--purple"></view><view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-right corner-ornament--gold"></view><text class="eyebrow">本地匿名树洞</text><text class="hero-title">吗喽的心声</text><text class="subtext">这里不会上传，也不会被其他用户看到。先把想说但暂时没人接住的话，放在本地。</text></view>
  <view class="ornament-card ornament-card--purple tree-hole-input"><view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--purple"></view><text class="section-title">我的本地树洞</text><textarea class="textarea" value="{{content}}" bindinput="onInput" placeholder-class="form-placeholder" placeholder="先放一句话在这里" /><view class="ornament-line"></view><text class="safe-note">请不要填写真实姓名、公司全称、联系方式或其他敏感信息。</text><button class="sticker-button green" bindtap="publishLocal">放进本地树洞</button></view>
  <view class="ornament-card"><text class="section-title">我的本地心声</text><view wx:if="{{!localPosts.length}}" class="empty-card local-empty"><text>你的本地树洞还空着。可以先放一句很小的话。</text></view><view wx:for="{{localPosts}}" wx:key="id" class="local-post paper-note"><text class="voice-id">{{item.anonymousId}}</text><text class="post-date">{{item.displayDate}}</text><text class="voice-text">{{item.content}}</text><text class="delete" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="deletePost">删除</text></view></view>
  <view class="floral-divider"><view class="floral-divider__line"></view><view class="floral-divider__dot red"></view><view class="floral-divider__dot green"></view><view class="floral-divider__line"></view></view><text class="group-title">精选心声墙</text>
  <view wx:for="{{featuredVoices}}" wx:key="id" class="ornament-card ornament-card--gold voice-card paper-note"><text class="voice-id">{{item.id}}</text><text class="voice-text">“{{item.text}}”</text><view class="reply-slip"><text>{{item.reply}}</text></view></view>
  <view class="empty-card voice-footer"><text>0.3B 的树洞只保存在本地，不会上传，也不会被其他用户看到。</text><text>真实匿名社区会在更后面的版本再考虑。</text></view>
</view>
